data.description:
ASSUMABLE LOAN 3.5% 
Great news for potential buyers! The seller is currently providing a generous $5,000 buyers incentive that will be available until the end of the year. Take advantage of this limited-time offer, which can significantly enhance your purchasing power. Don't miss out on this valuable opportunity!''


You will love this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom ranch house, it offers modern upgrades and high-end finishes throughout. The kitchen features stunning granite countertops, a gas stove, and upgraded appliances, making it a dream for any home chef. The great room boasts a cozy fireplace, perfect for gathering with friends and family. 

One unique feature of this home is the fourth bedroom, which serves as an in-law suite, providing privacy and convenience for guests or extended family. The open concept design creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, with the back of the house opening up to a covered deck, ideal for outdoor entertaining or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. 

Additionally, this house offers ample storage space with a built-in crawl space and a 10x30 concrete pad, perfect for a workshop or additional storage needs. The circular driveway provides plenty of parking for you and your guests. 

As a resident of The Retreat at Storm Branch, you'll 
have access to the HOA amenities, including a resort
-style pool and picturesque walking trails. The 
community's beautiful entrance adds to the overall appeal and charm of this neighborhood. 
  
Overall, this home offers a combination of functionality, style, and comfort, making it the perfect place for you and your loved ones to call home.
This stunning property offers a spacious 1 acre lot. Talk about LOCATION! You will find easy access to SRS; Downtown Augusta; minutes to Aiken!

3.5% assumable FHA loan.
